features: SPACIOUS STORAGE: The 3-tier shoe shelves provide ample room for up to 12 pairs of shoes. Tiers spaced 6.7" apart fit sneakers, heels, slippers. The bottom shelf is perfect for flats and slippers. Satisfies daily storage needs.

DURABLE MATERIAL: Kitsure shoe rack for closet floor is crafted with rust-proof coated metal tubes and sturdy metal frames to ensure durability and stability, preventing deformation over time. The thick, non-woven fabric is also made to last, resisting damage from regular use.

EASY ASSEMBLY: Kitsure provides step-by-step instructions and installation video to ensure quick and easy tool-free assembly. With only 4 steps you can easily set up this shoe rack organizer without screws or any other tools.

STACKABLE DESIGN: Kitsure closet shoe organizer features a stackable design that is perfect for customizing storage to fit your space. You can pile up 2 or more racks to organize your shoes, bags, suitcases, and more in a limited space.

MULTI-PURPOSE USE: With its compact size, this free-standing shoe rack fits seamlessly into small spaces around the home like garages, walk-in closets, and living rooms. Make the most of tight storage areas with this versatile Kitsure closet shoe rack.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great And Sturdy Shoe Rack!
reviews.reviewText: This is a great shoe rack! Materials are very high quality, solid, and durable. The setup was quick and easy! This is very light weight as well! This can hold other items as well. This is very easy to clean once the shoes put some dirt on it. Great value all around!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great, lightweight shoe (and other storage) solution
reviews.reviewText: This shoe rack was gigantic and fairly easy to assemble. It feels very sturdy, yet lightweight and you can customize where you put the taller boot shelf (I have mine on the bottom). I am using mine in the closet to store many pairs of shoes, but I am also using several of the higher shelves for board games. The hooks are also useful for hanging jackets or umbrellas on the side. I am very satisfied with the cost and quality.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Sturdy, Sturdy, Sturdy!
reviews.reviewText: This rack is amazing! I originally ordered it for shoes, but when it arrived and we put it together, I decided to turn it into a storage rack since it is so strong and durable. As you can see in the photos, I placed three heavy containers on it and it did not even buckle. I have a heavy tool kit on the bottle and just have not decided what to put in the middle – but I am certain it will hold it. This is a great rack with heavy canvas and it looks good! It’s not cheaply made and was super easy to put together. Directions are very easy. Highly recommend this for shoes or storage!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Maybe not quite as advertised
reviews.reviewText: Listen, was it easy to assemble? Yes. Is it sturdy? So far so good. Will it hold 16 pairs of shoes? Maybe if they were all toddler shoes. Definitely not adult shoes. In the pictures top row is 3 pairs of 10.5 women's shoes. Middle row 2 pairs of men's size 12 tennis shoes. No real room for another pair of anything there. And if you pay attention to the advert pic and compare to the attached pics, again, no real room for shoes unless flats, flip flops not as they show in picture.Will I use it? Sure. Am I satisfied? As far as holding shoes, yes. As far as it being as advertised, not completely. If you're ok with that, get it for yourself as well. If you would rather have a product exactly as advertised, keep looking.
